---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Hindalco">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Purpose</h2>
        <p>
          Totalis is committed to protecting the privacy of every individual who
          visits
          <a
            href="https://www.Totaliswindows.com"
            class="text-blue-600 underline">www.Totaliswindows.com</a
          >
          (the “Website”). This Privacy Policy sets out how personal data we collect
          from you, or that you provide to us, will be handled through your use of
          the Website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Definitions</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li><strong>“we” / “us” / “our”</strong> means Totalis</li>
          <li><strong>Website</strong> means www.Totaliswindows.com</li>
          <li>
            <strong>“you” / “your”</strong> means any person who visits our website
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Scope of Application</h2>
        This policy will be applicable to all personally identifiable information
        that you provide to Totalis while visiting or using the website. This website
        contains links to other sites. Please be aware that we are not responsible
        for the content or privacy practices of such other sites. We encourage our
        users to be aware when they leave our site and to read the privacy statements
        of any other site that collects personally identifiable information.
        <br />
        Totalis expressly reserves the right to change this Privacy Policy periodically
        in future which will be exercised at it sole discretion, and at such intervals
        of its choosing the right without prior notice to the users. Users shall
        review our Privacy Policy available at the Website regularly to be sure you
        are fully updated with our current practices and procedures in this area.
        Your continued use of the Website will be subject to the then-current Privacy
        Policy.
        <br />
        The following discloses our information gathering and dissemination practices
        for the Website:
        <br />
        Overview: As part of the normal operation of the Website, we collect and,
        in some cases, may disclose personally identifiable information about you.
        This Privacy Policy describes the personally identifiable information we
        collect about you and what may happen to that information.
        <br />
        By accepting this Privacy Policy and our Terms of Use, you expressly consent
        to our use and disclosure of your personally identifiable information in
        the manner prescribed in this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy is incorporated
        into and is subject to the conditions of the Terms of Use and governs all
        use of the Website by You.
        <br />
        We may collect your name, address, email address, telephone number, and other
        personally identifiable information you submit on the Website. Such personally
        identifiable information will not be posted in areas of the Website viewable
        by the public or users of the Site.
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Data Gathering</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">
          4.1 Collection of Information
        </h3>
        <p>We may collect personal information when you:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Email or contact us via the Website</li>
          <li>Submit enquiries or other forms</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">
          4.2 Our Use of Your Information
        </h3>
        <p>
          We use this data to improve your experience, deliver requested
          services, and tailor the Website to your needs.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">
          4.3 Disclosure of Your Information
        </h3>
        <p>We may disclose your data in the following situations:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>To comply with legal obligations or government requests</li>
          <li>
            To our affiliates or third-party service providers under
            confidentiality terms
          </li>
          <li>In business transfers (merger, acquisition, etc.)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, due to
          technical or legal constraints, full privacy cannot be guaranteed.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">
          4.4 Changing Your Personal Information
        </h3>
        <p>
          We retain personal data for legal or operational reasons even after a
          deletion request. Complete erasure is not always possible due to
          backups and constraints.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-1">4.5 Use of Cookies</h3>
        <p>
          The Website may use cookies to enhance functionality, analyze
          behavior, and customize content. Cookies do not identify users
          personally but may identify devices. You can disable cookies via your
          browser settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Security</h2>
        <p>
          Totalis uses reasonable security measures to protect your data but
          cannot guarantee complete security. Use of the Website is at your own
          risk.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Any future updates will be posted on this page. Your continued use of
          the Website constitutes your agreement to such changes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">7. Legal Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          This Website is owned by Totalis and intended for general
          informational purposes. All content is based on Indian law and is
          provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.
        </p>
        <p>
          Totalis is not responsible for external links or damages from site
          usage. Content cannot be reused commercially without prior written
          permission. Any disputes will be subject to the jurisdiction of the
          courts at Mumbai, India.
        </p>
        <p>
          For queries, contact us at <a
            href="mailto:Totalis.care@adityabirla.com"
            class="text-blue-600 underline">Totalis.care@adityabirla.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
